{"id":1734299,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-20T13:27:22.802Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1734299,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Rahimah Tanpa Rahim","overview":"# The Imperfect Woman  The story follows Rahimah (Puteri Aishah) who has MRKH syndrome. Rahimah is a caring and kind-hearted person to everyone around her. Despite her daily life being constantly scorned by her stepmother, Mak Aini (Lizza Abdullah), Rahimah continues to try to adjust to her village life by helping her neighbors. At the same time, Rahimah's father, Pak Akob (Badrul Muhayat), is frequently seen being intimate with his daughter's close friend, Shida (Diana Dee DFKL). Rahimah senses this behavior, but whenever she tries to tell Mak Aini, her stepmother becomes angry and doesn't believe her. Rahimah later meets Jauhar (Azlee Khairi), the founder of an NGO for troubled youth. There is something about Rahimah's sincerity and innocence that moves Jauhar to try to help her. However, because the problem involves her family, Rahimah fears the family's honor will be compromised and tries to distance herself from Jauhar.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/opvCADWiCotJsXAIYURwVp1LF74.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":86646,"logo_path":null,"name":"Country & Universal Sdn Bhd","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Rahimah Tanpa Rahim","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1335398,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Azlee Khairi","original_name":"Azlee Khairi","popularity":0.1497,"profile_path":"/tbfYHssqJ4WnoVSCDWJWEtw9ns5.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5d8e94b92a8742883248c9","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1738855,"known_f